latestPosts.caption:
For Amer Spring/Summer ’25, we found our rhythm in the heart of Amer Fort—under its grand arches, across sunlit terraces, through timeworn courtyards, along the limestone-veranda walls, within the mirrored splendor of Sheesh Mahal, and behind the patterned doors of Ganga Pol.

Spring arrives in Eka’s ethereal layers—crafted diaphanous textiles that echo the grace of movement itself.

We pinned location in Amer fort, just outside Jaipur, spending days immersed in its beauty - studying the motifs, breaking down the colors, and dancing through the landscape of history and nostalgia.
